        <li>e-Reader cards are either Japanese or English.</li>
        <li>Japanese e-Reader only works with Japanese GBA games and can only read Japanese e-Reader cards.</li>
        <li>English e-Reader only works with English GBA games and can only read English e-Reader cards.</li>
        <li>French, Italian, Spanish, German GBA games can't read e-Reader cards.</li>
