  <h3>Spin-Off Games</h3>

  <h5>GBA: Pokémon Pinball Ruby & Sapphire</h5>
  <div>It exists in 3 versions based on region. They are all compatible between each other. They can't communicate with other Pokémon games.</div>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="bold">Japan:</span> Japanese language</li>
    <li><span class="bold">The Americas and Asia:</span> English language</li>
    <li><span class="bold">Europe and Oceania:</span> English, French, German, Italian or Spanish (Changeable)</li>
  </ul>

  <h5>GBA: Pokémon Mystery Dungeon: Red/Blue Rescue Team</h5>
  <div>3 versions of Red Rescue Team, and 4 versions of Blue Rescue Team, exist. They are based on region. They can only directly communicate with games of the same region. They can't communicate with other Pokémon games.</div>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="bold">Japan:</span> Japanese language</li>
    <li><span class="bold">The Americas, Asia and Oceania:</span> English language</li>
    <li><span class="bold">Europe:</span> English, French, German, Italian or Spanish (Can't be changed after initial selection)</li>
    <li><span class="bold">Korea (Blue Rescue Team only):</span> Korean language</li>
  </ul>
